{"tid":1323784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲定今個禮拜六為我愛香港日","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T12:07:57.000Z","uid":198684,"like":5,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b54e0ea10b951c889de6f45717c89745aeb6abaa","tid":1323784,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"轉發<br />\n<br />\n我們今個星期六20/7/2019定一個我愛香港世界日。在當曰穿上紅色丅裇或手綁紅布或 絲帶上班或去街。不須要任何單張或旗。不須要遊行、在中國, 在香港，在台灣，在世界各地的香港人或熱愛香港而出一分力。去表示我們真的熱愛香港。不用粗言穢語、不用暴力。對每一個在當天穿上紅衣的人說聲我愛香港。我們要以無聲勝有聲，以和平和愛心去寬恕曾經破壞過香港的人。用我們紅色的愛火去溶解昨天互相的不信任.將昨天的仇恨化作團結的力量。向全世界各地去表揚香港的真善美。<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳，香港人多謝你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望真係不要粗言穢語 不要暴力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a3c1dcdf3ca7a0263ed381d90f4f3f4e79d4cd","tid":1323784,"uid":198684,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4SfPxv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4SfPxv.png&h=5e7eabb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n百九幾年冇傾過計既藍絲前同事sd黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7a3b815e3849eef0f9669931a2fb714c9dd782","tid":1323784,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7a2ab43d2f91ca06911e2b11715a2da4596cf4d1","tid":1323784,"uid":28765,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:13:37.000Z","msg":"變左紅絲"},{"pid":"c8c8def5347be2af60f31df0f4b2dc43022bd61c","tid":1323784,"uid":198684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a2ab43d2f91ca06911e2b11715a2da4596cf4d1","tid":1323784,"uid":28765,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"rep